@startuml State - Reservations

skinparam stateFontSize 13
skinparam stateArrowFontSize 11
skinparam roundcorner 8

[*] --> PENDING_PAYMENT : CreateReservation called

PENDING_PAYMENT --> CONFIRMED  : payment.booking.done\n(status=SUCCESS)
PENDING_PAYMENT --> CANCELLED  : payment.booking.done\n(status=FAILED/EXPIRED)\nor stale cleanup by scheduler

CONFIRMED --> CHECKED_IN : Driver checks in\nwithin 1 hour
CONFIRMED --> EXPIRED    : expires_at < now()\n(expiry scheduler)

CHECKED_IN --> COMPLETED : Driver checks out

COMPLETED --> [*]
EXPIRED   --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

@enduml
